OL,3,CWholesale price of Guernsey milk
OL,4,Cincreases by 4.4%
OL,6,FThe wholesale price of milk in
OL,7,FGuernsey increases by 4.4% as from
OL,8,Ftoday (Sunday 5 January).
OL,10,FBosses at Guernsey Dairy say the
OL,11,Fincrease, which is in line with
OL,12,Finflation, reflects rising costs and
OL,13,Fthe ongoing need for investment.
OL,15,FMark Thompson, Chairman of the Dairy
OL,16,FManagement Board, said "Every effort
OL,17,Fwas being made to contain increases,
OL,18,Fbut rising costs inevitably had to be
OL,19,Fpassed on to customers."
