OL,3,CWholesale price of Guernsey milk
OL,4,Cincreases by 4.4%
OL,6,FThe wholesale price is what the dairy
OL,7,Fcharges for the milk that is supplied
OL,8,Fto shops and via doorstep deliveries.
OL,9,FIt is then up to the retailers on
OL,10,Fwhether they increase the price of the
OL,11,Fmilk in shops.
OL,13,FGuernsey Dairy last increased the
OL,14,Fwholesale price of its milk by 4% in
OL,15,FJuly 2024.
